document.discussion_title: A Startling Fact about Easy 1 Up Uncovered
document.topic_text: Easy 1up has no retailable services or products, with affiliates only able to market Easy 1upward affiliate membership itself. Once registered, Easy 1up affiliates gift in between $25 to $500 to the affiliate who have recruited them. Bundled with each gifting payment is the following: -$25 payment - MULTILEVEL MARKETING Basics course and Affiliate KickStarter video series
